juniDs3Agent.name: juniDs3Agent

revisions.description: DS3-MIB: Replaced SMIv1 'groups' (RFC1407-MIB) with SMIv2 conformance groups (DS3-MIB).
Juniper-DS3-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Juniper-DS3-MIB: Added far end port number, generator number and carrier support.
DS3-MIB: Added far end support. Juniper-DS3-MIB: Added far end support.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniDs3Agent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniDs3Agent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the DS3 component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniDs3AgentV1.name: juniDs3AgentV1
juniDs3AgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component was supported in JUNOSe 1.0 system releases.
juniDs3AgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for line type and cell scrambler objects.

juniDs3AgentV2.name: juniDs3AgentV2
juniDs3AgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component was supported in JUNOSe 1.1 thru JUNOSe 2.5 system
        releases.
juniDs3AgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for DSU configuration objects.

juniDs3AgentV3.name: juniDs3AgentV3
juniDs3AgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component was supported in JUNOSe 2.6 and subsequent JUNOSe
        2.x system releases.
juniDs3AgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for dynamic DS3 interface objects.

juniDs3AgentV4.name: juniDs3AgentV4
juniDs3AgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component was supported in JUNOSe 3.x system releases.
juniDs3AgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when far end support was added to the Juniper-DS3-MIB.

juniDs3AgentV5.name: juniDs3AgentV5
juniDs3AgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component was supported in JUNOSe 4.0 system releases.
juniDs3AgentV5.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added to the Juniper-DS3-MIB for far end port number, generator number and carrier.

juniDs3AgentV6.name: juniDs3AgentV6
juniDs3AgentV6.productrelease:
Version 6 of the DS3 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS3 component is supported in JUNOSe 4.1 and subsequent system
        releases.
juniDs3AgentV6.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS3 application in JUNOSe.
